text: The following is a list of naturalized (or naturalised) basketball players who have represented their naturalised country at a FIBA international tournament. The list includes players both past and present after they have represented their new nation at least once. This list only includes players who have acquired the legal nationality of a country by naturalization or by any other means after the age of 16. ==Female players (By country)== Note: This list is
